ActPilotage Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of DONALD WILLIAM JAMES MARSHALL of Victoria, British Columbia, to be a member of the Pacific Pilotage Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Karen A. Horcher, whose term has expired.
